OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782827279
OL,3,CCouncil urged to reconsider closure of
OL,4,Cday care centre
OL,6,FCampaigners say the closure of
OL,7,FBrighton's last council-run day care
OL,8,Fcentre will be a disaster for those
OL,9,Fwho use it.
OL,11,FBrighton & Hove City Council is
OL,12,Fconsidering closing Wellington House -
OL,13,Fa facility which caters for adults
OL,14,Fwith complex learning disabilities -
OL,15,Fto save around #400,000.
OL,17,FIt's said the closure will only go
OL,18,Fahead, if suitable provision can be
OL,19,Ffound elsewhere for all 21 adults who
OL,20,Fcurrently use it.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
