CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782827279
OL,3,CCouncil urged to reconsider closure of
OL,4,Cday care centre
OL,6,FBut families of those in its care have
OL,7,Ftold ITV Meridian that adequate,
OL,8,Falternative options are not on the
OL,9,Ftable.
OL,11,FLou Vaughan, whose brother, Matt, has
OL,12,Fbeen going to Wellington House for 10
OL,13,Fyears, said the closure would remove
OL,14,Fhis "only interaction each week with
OL,15,Fhis peers".
OL,17,F"He goes three days a week," she said.
OL,18,F"Without Wellington House he wouldn't
OL,19,Fhave any interaction with his peers.
OL,21,F"It would just be with his carers."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
