FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782827279
OL,3,CCouncil urged to reconsider closure of
OL,4,Cday care centre
OL,6,FThe sentiment was shared by others who
OL,7,Fhad gathered to protest against the
OL,8,Fplans outside Hove Town Hall on Monday.
OL,10,FAnthony Hammond's sister has spent 40
OL,11,Fyears of her life visiting Wellington
OL,12,FHouse.
OL,14,FHe described the centre as a "mainstay
OL,15,Fof her life", adding its closure would
OL,16,Fhave a "major impact" on his sister.
OL,18,F"She sees all her friends," he said.
OL,19,F"She loves the staff to bits and it's
OL,20,Fa place where she needs to go."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
