FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782827279
OL,3,CCouncil urged to reconsider closure of
OL,4,Cday care centre
OL,6,FBrighton & Hove Councillor Mitchie
OL,7,FAlexander acknowledged the closure
OL,8,Fwould be "upsetting and unsettling"
OL,9,Ffor service users.
OL,11,F"But there will be provision available
OL,12,Ffor each and every one of the 21
OL,13,Fpeople that go to Wellington House,"
OL,14,Fshe added.
OL,16,F"It will be in a different place, but
OL,17,Fit will be as good a quality"
OL,19,FA public consultation on the closure
OL,20,Fof Wellington House is open until
OL,21,FTuesday, July 7.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
